comments: Curry (DAL) and Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) moves laterally into Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Curry (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Lowry (TOR) at the start of the drive.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lowry (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) makes contact to Brunson's (DAL) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Brunson (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Lowry (TOR) as Lowry goes to but not through Brunson.
After communicating with the replay center, the call on the court of the ball touching Brunson last before going out of bounds is confirmed.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) briefly engage and separate off ball during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) briefly engage and separate off ball in the post.
VanVleet (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Brunson (DAL) on the rebound.  VanVleet (TOR) and Porzingis (DAL) make incidental contact as they go for the loose ball.
After communicating with the replay center, the call on the court of Dallas ball is overturned.
Porzingis (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he collapses his forearm to absorb the contact during the driving shot attempt by Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Davis (TOR) cleanly deflects the pass away from Finney-Smith (DAL).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Davis (TOR) loses control of the ball out of bounds.
After Lowry (TOR) initially makes clean contact with the ball, he continues to engage and makes leg contact that trips Porzingis (DAL).
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Porzingis (DAL) after his pass and doesn't affect Porzingis' ability to defend the shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) and Finney-Smith (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Finney-Smith (DAL) commits a take foul on Boucher (TOR).
